verses.text: Blessed \w be|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H8085"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w who|strong="H3068"\w* teacheth \w my|strong="H8085"\w* hands \w to|strong="H0413"\w* fight, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H8085"\w* fingers \w to|strong="H0413"\w* war.

\w My|strong="H3605"\w* mercy, \w and|strong="H0935"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* refuge: \w my|strong="H3605"\w* support, \w and|strong="H0935"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* deliverer: \w My|strong="H3605"\w* protector, \w and|strong="H0935"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H5650"\w* hoped \w in|strong="H0935"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*: \w who|strong="H3605"\w* subdueth \w my|strong="H3605"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w under|strong="H0935"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*.

Lord, \w what|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H0776"\w* \w man|strong="H5315"\w*, \w that|strong="H3588"\w* thou art made known \w to|strong="H4191"\w* \w him|strong="H4191"\w*? \w or|strong="H4191"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* son \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w man|strong="H5315"\w*, \w that|strong="H3588"\w* thou makest account \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w him|strong="H4191"\w*?
Man \w is|strong="H3820"\w* \w like|strong="H7307"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* vanity: \w his|strong="H5921"\w* days pass away \w like|strong="H7307"\w* \w a|strong="H5921"\w* shadow.

Lord, bow \w down|strong="H3027"\w* thy heavens \w and|strong="H3027"\w* descend: touch \w the|strong="H3605"\w* mountains \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w they|strong="H3117"\w* \w shall|strong="H3117"\w* smoke.

Send forth lightning, \w and|strong="H0776"\w* thou shalt scatter \w them|strong="H0413"\w*: shoot \w out|strong="H0413"\w* thy arrows, \w and|strong="H0776"\w* thou shalt trouble \w them|strong="H0413"\w*.

\w Put|strong="H3381"\w* forth thy hand \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w on|strong="H3068"\w* high, \w take|strong="H3381"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w out|strong="H4480"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* deliver \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* many waters: \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* hand \w of|strong="H3068"\w* strange children:

\w Whose|strong="H2098"\w* \w mouth|strong="H5315"\w* hath \w spoken|strong="H0413"\w* vanity: \w and|strong="H1242"\w* \w their|strong="H5375"\w* right hand \w is|strong="H5315"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* right hand \w of|strong="H1870"\w* iniquity.

\w To|strong="H0413"\w* thee, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* sing \w a|strong="H3068"\w* new canticle: \w on|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* psaltery \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w an|strong="H3068"\w* instrument \w of|strong="H3068"\w* ten strings \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* sing \w praises|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H0413"\w* thee.
\w Who|strong="H0776"\w* givest salvation \w to|strong="H0776"\w* kings: \w who|strong="H0776"\w* hast redeemed thy servant David \w from|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* malicious sword:

\w Deliver|strong="H6869"\w* \w me|strong="H5315"\w*, \w And|strong="H3068"\w* \w rescue|strong="H5315"\w* \w me|strong="H5315"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* hand \w of|strong="H3068"\w* strange children; \w whose|strong="H8034"\w* \w mouth|strong="H5315"\w* hath spoken vanity: \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* \w right|strong="H6666"\w* hand \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w right|strong="H6666"\w* hand \w of|strong="H3068"\w* iniquity:

\w Whose|strong="H3605"\w* sons \w are|strong="H5650"\w* \w as|strong="H5315"\w* new plants \w in|strong="H5315"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* youth: \w Their|strong="H3605"\w* daughters decked \w out|strong="H3605"\w*, adorned round \w about|strong="H3605"\w* \w after|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* similitude \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w a|strong="H3588"\w* temple:
Their storehouses full, flowing out of this into that. Their sheep fruitful in young, abounding in their goings forth:
Their oxen fat. There is no breach of wall, nor passage, nor crying out in their streets.
They have called the people happy, that hath these things: but happy is that people whose God is the Lord.
